- Apparmor enable in kernel cmdline
- Set EDITOR=nvim
- Save root packages list to file, read it for pacstrap
- Brave browser and update script (pacman hook)
- Pacman hook to setup apparmor profiles
- postsync.d folder for pacman hooks
- Save .gitconfig instead of setup commands
- amg-laptop: "systemctl mask dev-tpmrm0.device"
- amg-pc: install nvidia-open and nvidia-utils
